name: Levi's Men's 501 Original Fit Jeans

name: Wrangler Men's Authentics Regular Fit Jean
description: The Wrangler Men's Authentics Regular Fit Jean offers a versatile and classic style for men. These jeans are made from durable cotton denim with a touch of stretch for added comfort. The regular fit provides a relaxed, easygoing silhouette with a traditional five-pocket design and a zip fly. The jeans feature Wrangler's signature stitching on the back pockets and a leather Wrangler patch on the waistband. Ideal for casual wear, these jeans offer a combination of comfort and style.
